glade <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/ukytherion.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kytherion</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 237<br> <font color=#E9D756>(9/16/01 5:01:20 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> /blink</span><hr size=1> I think I'm going to be sick. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#575757><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/ulanarie.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lanarie</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://broucek.net/mtg_mst3k/h_hang10.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 127<br> <font color=#E9D756>(9/16/01 5:09:16 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The sad situation we find ourselves in...</span><hr size=1> You can go to Canada, Just don't ever try to come back.<br>
<br>
  Millions of men and women have stood in your position, a large majority of them answered the call to serve their country.  This country was made strong by the patriotism and selfless service to their country. Have you bothered to think of the sacrifices these people made so you can enjoy your freedom.<br>
